{"tid":2168494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"講真巴塞要重建 可以諗諗佢 — Luuk de jong（內含詳盡分析）","createTime":"2020-08-21T20:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T01:19:13.000Z","uid":343520,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"78086af8ff697ae66e63c2278d3d90efd7f30fad","tid":2168494,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:13:53.000Z","msg":"首先，盧卡迪莊呢位球員既實力係有目共睹，剛剛已經挺身而出，連入兩球拯救西維爾於水深火熱之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種領袖氣質絕對係巴塞自佩奧爾退役後，咁多年黎一直都缺乏既，大家成日都話美斯輸波頭dupdup，帶領唔到球隊呢個問題，簽入盧卡迪莊就可以解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，盧卡迪莊本身已經踢緊西甲，唔存在要適應既問題，而且買入同聯賽球員可以削弱對手，等於未開季已經多左六分優勢，下季皇馬要追又難左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，買入佢既難度比買big name易好多，方便投放資金去其他位協助重建，大家都知道西維爾不嬲都做開selling club，所有球員都有個價，唔存在非賣品既問題，盧卡迪莊既價錢一定合理、公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四，大家都知道巴塞新領隊朗奴高文係荷蘭人，而盧卡迪莊亦係同鄉，將帥同聲同氣，對戰術理解，球員指令都會更清晰明確，百利而無一害，而且迪比，雲迪碧克呢啲荷蘭兵已經係巴塞目標，連同本身既法蘭基迪莊，可以組成荷蘭新世代四人幫，重建巴塞黃金一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第五，巴塞既前鋒蘇亞雷斯本身都係荷甲出道，繼續用荷甲前鋒可以話係一種傳承，而且隊中有兩個迪莊，落到場用波時可以大嗌：「迪莊攞波！」擾亂對手，算係戰術上既小聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dw2tJ0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdw2tJ0i.jpg&h=d9acabf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之一句講晒，巴塞，唔買無所謂，你損失！"},{"pid":"007c0be0de1461f56d729139dd2dd54de7f5a47e","tid":2168494,"uid":14126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71544912bd4ae67ac8384959cff837c55b57a7d1","tid":2168494,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007c0be0de1461f56d729139dd2dd54de7f5a47e","tid":2168494,"uid":14126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"你都迷迪莊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711716c4891868ab2c2bc8c103dcd94c1aa1a35e","tid":2168494,"uid":46090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:21:17.000Z","msg":"第五真係好屈"},{"pid":"9182ea81ecba7795881679af3d832eede6f05f96","tid":2168494,"uid":165665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:23:25.000Z","msg":"第五個點破<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8578f382f9f8643aa3b4007d1a0f6534151c363a","tid":2168494,"uid":158145,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:25:07.000Z","msg":"真，朗奴高文唔係幾掂<br />\n應該做半季就走<br />\n不過L de jong 未有執教經驗<br />\n我驚鎮唔住隊內班大佬<br />\n第一次就教大會<br />\n會唔會復製第一次教波既哥迪奧拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35682cf5ec0b0c1573f4c5bf594b7ef0a5021dd3","tid":2168494,"uid":14126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71544912bd4ae67ac8384959cff837c55b57a7d1","tid":2168494,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007c0be0de1461f56d729139dd2dd54de7f5a47e","tid":2168494,"uid":14126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T20:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown